iles/images/shop/device-gallery/30-megld.jpg" target="_blank">Gold Nexus 6 Skin</a></div><div class="rsContent"><a class="rsImg" href="../sites/default/files/images/shop/device-gallery/31-mtblk.jpg" target="_blank">Matte Black Nexus 6 Skin</a></div><div class="rsContent"><a class="rsImg" href="../sites/default/files/images/shop/device-gallery/32-metit.jpg" target="_blank">Titanium Nexus 6 Skin</a></div><div class="rsContent"><a class="rsImg" href="../sites/default/files/images/shop/device-gallery/33-cfwht.jpg" target="_blank">White Carbon Nexus 6 Skin</a></div><div class="rsContent"><a class="rsImg" href="../sites/default/files/images/shop/device-gallery/34-megld.jpg" target="_blank">Gold Nexus 6 Skin</a></div><div class="rsContent"><a class="rsImg" href="../sites/default/files/images/shop/device-gallery/35-wdmhg.jpg" target="_blank">Mahogany Nexus 6 Skin</a></div></aside></div></div></div><div class="group group--borderless group--device-features"><div class="group__inner"><div class="group group--device-features-header"><div class="group__inner"><h2 class="device-features-header"><div class="logo"><span class="inner">ACellShop</span></div> guarantees</h2></div></div><div class="taxonomy-term--device-features taxonomy-term--full taxonomy-term--device-features--full taxonomy-term taxonomy-term--nexus-6-quality taxonomy-term--device-features--quality">
    <div class="group group-content" id="taxonomy-term-device-features-full-group-content"><div class="group__inner"><div class="text-body">
  <h3 class="field field--name-title-field field--type-text field--label-hidden">
    High-Quality Material  </h3>
<div class="taxonomy-term-description">At dbrand, we use only Authentic 3M vinyl on our Nexus 6 skins. That means, when you decide to take off your Nexus 6 wrap to put on a new one, there is never any adhesive residue left on your device. Guaranteed. We are committed to providing our customers with uncompromising quality. You can relax. We only use the highest grade materials on the planet.</div></div>
  <figure class="field field--name-field-image field--type-image field--label-hidden">
    <img src="../sites/default/files/images/device-features/quality.jpg" width="800" height="500" alt="" />  </figure>
</div></div></div>
<div class="taxonomy-term--device-features taxonomy-term--full taxonomy-term--device-features--full taxonomy-term taxonomy-term--nexus-6-precision taxonomy-term--device-features--precision">
    <div class="group group-content" id="taxonomy-term-device-features-full-group-content--2"><div class="group__inner"><div class="text-body">
  <h3 class="field field--name-title-field field--type-text field--label-hidden">
    Unrivaled Precision  </h3>
<div class="taxonomy-term-description">Looking for the best Nexus 6 skin possible? You've come to the right place. The pictures don't lie. Our Nexus 6 skins offer the most precise fit on the market. Only ACellShop offers a flawless cutout for the <em>nexus</em> letters on the back of your device, plus we have 'X' Only and 'No Nexus' versions available at no extra cost. We've meticulously measured each of the cutouts on our skins for the Nexus 6 over a thousand times, down to the micro millimeter. It literally isn't possible to find a better fitting, higher quality Nexus 6 skin than the one you'll find at dbrand. We are the definition of precision.</div></div>
  <figure class="field field--name-field-image field--type-image field--label-hidden">
    <img src="../sites/default/files/images/device-features/precision.jpg" width="800" height="500" alt="" />  </figure>
</div></div></div>
<div class="taxonomy-term--device-features taxonomy-term--full taxonomy-term--device-features--full taxonomy-term taxonomy-term--nexus-6-variety taxonomy-term--device-features--variety">
    <div class="group group-content" id="taxonomy-term-device-features-full-group-content--3"><div class="group__inner"><div class="text-body">
  <h3 class="field field--name-title-field field--type-text field--label-hidden">
    Our Variety, Your Choice  </h3>
<div class="taxonomy-term-description">Our Nexus 6 decals come in six true-textured finishes: Carbon Fiber, Brushed Titanium, Matte, Leather, powder-coated True Colour, and Wood. You won't find a more authentic texture among any of our competitors. Our wraps for the Nexus 6 are available in a custom-selected range of exclusive, textured materials. From black leather to gold, powder-coated red to matte white, even mahogany... you'll be sure to find one that matches your style.</div></div>
  <figure class="field field--name-field-image field--type-image field--label-hidden">
    <img src="../sites/default/files/images/device-features/variety.jpg" width="800" height="500" alt="" />  </figure>
</div></div></div>
<div class="taxonomy-term--device-features taxonomy-term--full taxonomy-term--device-features--full taxonomy-term taxonomy-term--nexus-6-mission taxonomy-term--device-features--mission">
    <div class="group group-content" id="taxonomy-term-device-features-full-group-content--4"><div class="group__inner"><div class="text-body">
  <h3 class="field field--name-title-field field--type-text field--label-hidden">
    Our Mission  </h3>
<div class="taxonomy-term-description">With other companies, what you see is never what you get. They hide behind poorly photoshopped images of their product. They mark up their prices with hidden taxes and excessive shipping costs. At dbrand, we've got nothing to hide. Taxes are included in the price and we ship worldwide. Our state-of-the-art website represents our hunger for a higher-caliber skin. Our mission is clear: To save the world from inferior skins, one device at a time.</div></div>
